                        <interp inst="t18350511-name-443" type="given" value="HUGH"></interp>HUGH CUNNINGHAM</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable G</hi> 36.) I took the prisoner.</p>
               <p>(Mrs. Humphreys, of No. 37, Compton-street, gave the prisoner a good character.)</p>
